chunk_content: Prerequisites- Read the When to use Azure OpenAI fine-tuning guide.- An Azure subscription - Create one for free.- An Azure AI hub resource.- An Azure AI project in Azure AI Studio.- An Azure OpenAI connection to a resource in a region where fine-tuning is supported.- Fine-tuning access requires Cognitive Services OpenAI Contributor role on the Azure OpenAI resource.- If you don't already have access to view quota and deploy models in Azure AI Studio you need more permissions.
